          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Pay our Homeland Heroes Act </b></p> <p>This bill provides FY2019 continuing appropriations for (1) the pay and allowances of members and employees of the U.S. Coast Guard, and (2) the salaries and expenses of law enforcement and customs and border protection officers within the Department of Homeland Security. </p> <p>The bill provides the continuing appropriations for any period during which interim or full-year appropriations for FY2019 are not in effect. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-01-28T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
